    <item>
      <title>德国大选领先者在极右翼支持下推动法案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/german-election-front-runner-takes-next-step-in-far-right-pivot</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管在全国大选前三周，抗议活动令德国陷入分裂，德国保守党领袖弗里德里希·梅尔茨仍坚持推进极右翼支持的严厉移民法案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/german-election-front-runner-takes-next-step-in-far-right-pivot</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 13:45:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰警方因 Pegasus 间谍软件案拘留前司法部长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/polish-police-detain-ex-justice-chief-in-pegasus-spyware-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五，波兰警方短暂拘留了前司法部长兹比格涅夫·齐奥布罗 (Zbigniew Ziobro)，试图强迫他在议会委员会上作证，该委员会将调查上届政府使用 Pegasus 间谍软件的情况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/polish-police-detain-ex-justice-chief-in-pegasus-spyware-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 13:00:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的资助禁令两天内结束，引发持续恐慌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/trump-s-federal-funding-freeze-sparks-lasting-panic-despite-omb-reversal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普总统连续一周发布行政命令后，这份备忘录于周一晚间发布，并在不到 48 小时后被撤销。但暂停所有联邦贷款和补助的命令在全国范围内引起了反响，从小型非营利组织到庞大的卫生机构。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/trump-s-federal-funding-freeze-sparks-lasting-panic-despite-omb-reversal</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罗马尼亚努力削减预算，避免极右翼势力崛起</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/romania-struggles-to-trim-budget-without-feeding-far-right-surge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗马尼亚总理马塞尔·乔拉库 (Marcel Ciolacu) 正在努力寻找 80 亿欧元（83 亿美元）的储蓄，因为他的政府正努力抵抗极右翼势力的崛起。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/romania-struggles-to-trim-budget-without-feeding-far-right-surge</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 12:51:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯竞标基地协议 愿帮助叙利亚重建</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/russia-offers-to-help-rebuild-syria-as-it-bids-for-deal-on-bases</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯政府一位高级中东政策顾问表示，俄罗斯愿意帮助叙利亚重建，同时继续寻求与叙利亚新领导层达成协议，以保留两个重要的军事基地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/russia-offers-to-help-rebuild-syria-as-it-bids-for-deal-on-bases</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 12:48:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国预算案在做出最新让步后仍面临议员们的激烈争论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/french-conference-committee-reaches-deal-on-2025-budget-bill</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国议员周五就 2025 年预算版本达成协议，为下周议会推翻政府的决战铺平了道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/french-conference-committee-reaches-deal-on-2025-budget-bill</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 12:31:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>雪佛龙开始使用“美国湾”来向特朗普致敬</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/chevron-starts-using-gulf-of-america-in-nod-to-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普下令美国重新命名雪佛龙公司后，该公司已开始在其盈利材料中使用“美国湾”而不是“墨西哥湾”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/chevron-starts-using-gulf-of-america-in-nod-to-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 12:10:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京允许高盛出售其在俄罗斯的业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/putin-allows-goldman-sachs-to-sell-its-business-in-russia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京允许高盛集团出售其在俄罗斯的业务，这使得该美国公司成为少数几家完全退出俄罗斯的西方银行之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/putin-allows-goldman-sachs-to-sell-its-business-in-russia</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 11:09:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国保守党暂停有争议的移民问题投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/german-conservatives-pause-controversial-vote-on-migration-bill</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国立法者正在就一项备受争议的移民法案寻求最后一刻的妥协，以使该提案能够在不需要极右翼支持的情况下继续推进。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/german-conservatives-pause-controversial-vote-on-migration-bill</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 10:15:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
